  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:316\">We detected an <a href=\"https://status.cloud.google.com/incidents/ow5i3PPK96RduMcb1SsW\"><strong>incident on Google Cloud</strong></a> on June 12th, 2025. Our teams immediately investigated, checking logs and metrics for all affected services.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:108\">The incident resulted in <strong>degraded performance and intermittent availability</strong> of Analytics Cloud between <strong>11:00 AM PDT and 12:30 PM PDT</strong>. We're pleased to confirm that <strong>no data was lost</strong> during this period. Service has since returned to normal.</p>\n\n<p data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:153\">We apologize for any disruption or inconvenience this may have caused to your operations. We continue to monitor our systems closely to ensure stability.</p>"
      },
